In article hess734959172swt1 hessswt1informatikunihamburgde Hauke Hess writes

 I wonder if it is possible for a parent window to paint over the area
 of its childs

Yes but its not an attribute of the window its an attribute of the
GC used to do the drawing  Set the subwindowmode to IncludeInferiors
rather than the default ClipByChildren

